long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides connected printer statuses
Purpose:
- The utility uses the user's printer address information to check the connection status with the printer
- After obtaining the printer's connection status, the utility will return connection status information to the user.
- Domain restriction utility allows use for internal project purposes
